{"thig7.1:0.1":"Therigatha 7.1 ","thig7.1:0.2":"Sattakanipata ","thig7.1:0.3":"Uttaratherigatha ","thig7.1:1.1":"“Musalani gahetvana, ","thig7.1:1.2":"dhannam kottenti manava; ","thig7.1:1.3":"Puttadarani posenta, ","thig7.1:1.4":"dhanam vindanti manava. ","thig7.1:2.1":"Ghatetha buddhasasane, ","thig7.1:2.2":"yam katva nanutappati; ","thig7.1:2.3":"Khippam padani dhovitva, ","thig7.1:2.4":"ekamantam nisidatha. ","thig7.1:3.1":"Cittam upatthapetvana, ","thig7.1:3.2":"ekaggam susamahitam; ","thig7.1:3.3":"Paccavekkhatha sankhare, ","thig7.1:3.4":"parato no ca attato”. ","thig7.1:4.1":"“Tassaham vacanam sutva, ","thig7.1:4.2":"patacaranusasanim; ","thig7.1:4.3":"Pade pakkhalayitvana, ","thig7.1:4.4":"ekamante upavisim. ","thig7.1:5.1":"Rattiya purime yame, ","thig7.1:5.2":"pubbajatimanussarim; ","thig7.1:5.3":"Rattiya majjhime yame, ","thig7.1:5.4":"dibbacakkhum visodhayim. ","thig7.1:6.1":"Rattiya pacchime yame, ","thig7.1:6.2":"tamokhandham padalayim; ","thig7.1:6.3":"Tevijja atha vutthasim, ","thig7.1:6.4":"kata te anusasani. ","thig7.1:7.1":"Sakkamva deva tidasa, ","thig7.1:7.2":"sangame aparajitam; ","thig7.1:7.3":"Purakkhatva vihassami, ","thig7.1:7.4":"tevijjamhi anasava”. ","thig7.1:8.1":"… Uttara theri …. "}